<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>Effective date: February 26, 2026</p>

<h2>Who We Are</h2>
<p>GOSQO AI Chat & Store Assistant is a Shopify application that provides AI-powered customer chat, inbox management, and product content optimization tools.</p>

<h2>Information We Access</h2>
<p>When installed, the app may access certain Shopify store data including store information, products, orders, and customer communication data as required to provide app functionality.</p>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Provide live chat and inbox functionality</li>
  <li>Generate AI-assisted responses and content suggestions</li>
  <li>Perform SEO audits and product content analysis</li>
  <li>Support billing and subscription management</li>
  <li>Maintain system security and reliability</li>
</ul>

<h2>AI Processing</h2>
<p>Some data may be processed by third-party AI service providers solely for the purpose of generating responses and content suggestions.</p>

<h2>Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
<p>Data is retained only as long as necessary to provide the service. Upon app uninstallation or verified deletion request, associated store data is deleted in accordance with Shopify requirements.</p>

<h2>Security</h2>
<p>We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect data, including encryption in transit and access controls.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>For privacy inquiries, contact: privacy@gosqo.com</p>

